  {
    "id": "f_csv_7f54a86cad",
    "slug": "all-of-my-works-are-steps-on-my-journey-a-struggle-for-truth-that-i-have-waged",
    "texto": "All of my works are steps on my journey, a struggle for truth that I have waged with pen, canvas, and materials. Overhead is a distant, radiant star, and the more I stretch to reach it, the further it recedes. But by the power of my spirit and my single-hearted pursuit of the path, I have clawed my way through the labyrinthine confusion of the world of people in an unstinting effort to approach even one step closer to the realm of the soul.",
